<NEW>

"Of course." Lord Elder said over the comlink. "I hope they will be
there shortly."

Even as LORD ELDER was speaking the Protohumans were disappearing from
view heading down a path down the mountainside. If they wanted to keep
an optic on the protohumans they would have to follow them. Or they
could wait for NIGHTSHIFT and the others to arrive.

(TAG)

- Preston
